title: VA_-_Still_Fresh-2008-UPE
description:
Spin Twist Records presents \&#039;Still Fresh\&#039;, compiled by Vaishiyas and DJ Intellifex.

DJ Intelliflex is one of Germany\&#039;s most talented progessive DJ\&#039;s, with regular bookings at festivals like Indian Spirit. Together they\&#039;ve compiled 9 progressive bombs from the Spintwist\&#039;s stable of artists such as; Day.Din and Fabio, Sonic Cube, Midimal including well established German pioneers such as Feuerhake and Magnetrixx to mention a few...

Last but not least two very exciting sideprojects: the Swiss based Motion Drive, who many might know as one half of the full on act Rumble Pack, and Germany\&#039;s Kaempfer and Dietze, the more groovy and progressive side of the rocking duo Protonica...

One of Spintwist\&#039;s freshest releases, with a guaranteed long shelflife!
